    <h2 id="email-addresses-18012022" class="govuk-heading-m">A better way to collect email addresses</h2>
    <p>MoJ Forms now includes a component specifically designed for collecting email addresses.</p>
    <p>The component follows the <a class="govuk-link" href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/patterns/email-addresses/">GOV.UK Design System pattern</a> for asking users for their email addresses. It looks like a standard text input but includes custom validation to ensure that what the user enters fits a valid email address format.</p>
